name: Create a new product
description:
In app should be possible create a new product in list
        - Must have a button New
        - Must have a screen to add information about product
        - Description, amount and unit value is a required field

steps.name: user click in button new in register product screen
screen to add information about a new product appears
the user fills the all fields and click in save button
the new product is add in register product screen
